{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Utils.HetHashtbl</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"union-find-lattice","href":"../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Utils","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"HetHashtbl","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>Most of this code is adapated from the OCaml Standard library's implementation of <code>Hashtbl</code>. It is just adapted for polymorphic types. I.E. a <code>'b t</code> hashtabl binding <code>'a key</code> to <code>('a,'b) value</code> (note that <code>'a</code> is quantified existantially here).</p><p>Copyright 1996 Institut National de Recherche en Informatique et en Automatique. distributed under the terms of the GNU Lesser General Public License version 2.1, with the special exception on linking described in the license</p>","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module-type anchored\" id=\"module-type-HETEROGENEOUS_HASHED_TYPE\"><a href=\"#module-type-HETEROGENEOUS_HASHED_TYPE\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <a href=\"module-type-HETEROGENEOUS_HASHED_TYPE/index.html\">HETEROGENEOUS_HASHED_TYPE</a></span><span> = <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module-type anchored\" id=\"module-type-HETEROGENEOUS_SEEDED_HASHED_TYPE\"><a href=\"#module-type-HETEROGENEOUS_SEEDED_HASHED_TYPE\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <a href=\"module-type-HETEROGENEOUS_SEEDED_HASHED_TYPE/index.html\">HETEROGENEOUS_SEEDED_HASHED_TYPE</a></span><span> = <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id